INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(7,'In the heart of the ancient city, the stone pathways echoed with the footsteps of countless generations that came before. In the heart of the city, the bustling markets were a treasure trove of unique finds and local craftsmanship. As the sun set over the ocean, painting the sky in shades of pink and gold, I felt a sense of peace wash over me.','https://www.naaree.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Adventure-Travel.jpg');
INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(8,'In the heart of the rainforest, the air was thick with humidity, and every step was a symphony of life. Beneath the forest canopy, the air was cool and refreshing, and the sound of rustling leaves was a symphony of nature. The scent of blooming flowers filled the air, a sweet perfume that seemed to dance on the breeze.','https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp6737875.jpg');
INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(8,'High in the mountains, the air was crisp and invigorating, and the snow-capped peaks stretched out as far as the eye could see. At the heart of the bustling square, a fountain danced with cascading water, a symbol of life and vitality. The scent of freshly baked bread wafted through the air as I stepped into the charming village bakery.','http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Hx4HUBJ8h3Q/UoUVF2hA8RI/AAAAAAAAFK8/5COGFe4zUYg/s1600/Atlantis+Paradise+Island,+Bahamas4.jpg');
INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(6,'In the heart of the city, the bustling markets were a treasure trove of unique finds and local craftsmanship. On the cobalt blue waters, dolphins danced in the waves, a playful reminder of the wonders of marine life. Beneath the surface of the clear blue sea, a vibrant world of corals and marine life unfolded before my eyes.','https://q2travel.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/HwangeElephantHideCropped-1030x441.jpg');
INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(1,'The centuries-old oak tree stood as a silent witness to the passage of time, its branches reaching out in all directions. Perched on a hilltop, the medieval castle offered panoramic views of the picturesque countryside below. Wandering through the bustling markets, I immersed myself in the vibrant colors, unique scents, and lively atmosphere.','http://foundtheworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Paradise-Island-6-1.jpg');
INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(4,'Among the ancient ruins, I could almost hear the whispers of history, the stories of those who came before. The scent of blooming flowers filled the air, a sweet perfume that seemed to dance on the breeze. In the midst of a lively festival, the streets were alive with music, dancing, and the joyous laughter of people celebrating.','https://www.croquelune-mariage.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/21-1.jpg');
INSERT INTO POSTS(USER_ID,DESCRIPTION,IMAGE_URL) VALUES(9,'Navigating the narrow alleyways of the old town, I stumbled upon a charming bookshop filled with literary treasures. Among the ancient ruins, I could almost hear the whispers of history, the stories of those who came before. In the heart of the city, the bustling markets were a treasure trove of unique finds and local craftsmanship.','http://www.cotswoldsadventures.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Rural-Landscape-Cotswolds.jpg');
